PrecisAppointment of Willie Gibbs, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of seven years; and designation of the said Willie Gibbs as the Chairperson of the National Parole Board, effective September 1, 1994.
